The frontend of VitalAI is built with a modern and responsive user interface designed to provide an intuitive healthcare analytics experience. It features interactive dashboards, animated UI components, real-time prediction forms, and visually appealing data representations to enhance user engagement and usability.

The application includes secure authentication pages, profile and settings management,prediction input forms, and detailed result visualization for cardiovascular risk analysis. Users can enter medical parameters through a clean and user-friendly interface, after which the frontend communicates with backend APIs to fetch AI-generated predictions instantly.

Built using modern web technologies, the frontend emphasizes responsiveness, accessibility, smooth navigation, and optimized performance across desktop and mobile devices. Additional enhancements such as dynamic charts, dark/light mode support, loading animations, and real-time feedback systems improve the overall user experience and make the platform feel professional and scalable.
